        <p style="font-size:var(--text-sm); color:var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">You're new to UPSC or just decided to prepare. You need to understand the exam first, then build a strong foundation.</p>

        <h4 style="color:var(--color-brand); margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Your First 4 Weeks:</h4>
        <ol style="font-size:var(--text-sm); margin-left:var(--space-5); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">
