          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);"><strong>Week 2:</strong> Start with <a href="/subjects/polity/">Polity</a> — read Foundation-level notes, then try 10 MCQs</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);"><strong>Week 3:</strong> Add <a href="/subjects/economy/">Economy</a> and <a href="/subjects/geography/">Geography</a> — Foundation notes + MCQs</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);"><strong>Week 4:</strong> Start daily current affairs on <a href="https://ujiyari.com/daily/" target="_blank">Ujiyari.com</a> (30 min/day)</li>
        </ol>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-3); flex-wrap:wrap;">
