        <ol style="font-size:var(--text-sm); margin-left:var(--space-5); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Read <strong>Prelims-level</strong> notes for each subject — facts, dates, numbers</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Take <a href="/prelims/">daily 10-question sprints</a> — build speed + accuracy</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Solve <a href="/pyq/">previous year questions</a> topic-wise — the best prep there is</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Take full mocks monthly — <a href="/prelims/">100-question timed tests</a></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Track weak subjects on <a href="/tracker/">Progress Tracker</a> — focus on lowest-scoring areas</li>
        </ol>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-3); flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="/prelims/" class="btn btn--accent btn--sm">Start Prelims Practice →</a>
          <a href="/study-plan/#prelims" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm">See 6-Month Plan</a>
